Function

process_data <- function(comp_name) {
  if (comp_name == "tko_vs_wt") {
    sample_name <- "HCT116_LBR_TMPO_LMNA_KO_HLTLad5_vs_HCT116_WT"
    gen_name <- "TKO vs WT"
  } else if (comp_name == "dko_vs_wt") {
    sample_name <- "HCT116_LBR_TMPO_KO_HLTd3_vs_HCT116_WT"
    gen_name <- "DKO vs WT"
  }

  chip_df <- read_csv(
    paste0(chip_dir, comp_name, "/hct116_", comp_name, "_", mod_name, "_ens_canon_promoter_only.csv")
  ) |>
    select(
      peak_id, gene_id, gene_symbol, gene_type, logFC, FDR
    ) |>
    mutate(
      db_status = case_when(
        (logFC >= 1 & FDR <= 0.05) ~ "increased",
        (logFC <= -1 & FDR <= 0.05) ~ "decreased",
        .default = "unchanged"
      )
    )

  rna_df <- read_csv(
    paste(rna_dir, sample_name, "/", sample_name, "_LFC", as.character(RNA_LFC), "_DESeq2_apeglm_res.csv", sep = "")
  ) |>
    select(
      gene_id, log2FoldChange, padj, regulation_level
    )

  merged_df <- inner_join(
    chip_df, rna_df,
    by = c("gene_id"),
    suffix = c("_chip", "_rna")
  ) |>
    mutate(
      genotype = gen_name
    )

  merged_df
}

Plot

custom_cols <- c(
  "sig_changed" = "#c51b8a",
  "unchanged" = "#999999"
)

plt <- ggplot(
  combined_df,
  aes(
    x = logFC,
    y = log2FoldChange
  )
) +
  geom_point(
    aes(
      x = logFC,
      y = log2FoldChange,
      color = status
    ),
    show.legend = FALSE,
    alpha = 0.5
  ) +
  geom_smooth(
    method = lm,
    se = TRUE,
    color = "black"
  ) +
  stat_cor(
    method = "spearman",
    show.legend = FALSE,
    label.x = -5,
    label.y = -5
  ) +
  coord_cartesian(
    xlim = c(-5, 5),
    ylim = c(-5, 5)
  ) +
  geom_hline(yintercept = c(-1, 1), linetype = "dotted", col = "black") +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(-1, 1), linetype = "dotted", col = "black") +
  scale_color_manual(values = custom_cols) +
  facet_wrap(
    ~genotype
  ) +
  labs(
    x = expression("log"[2] * "(fold change) ChIP-seq"),
    y = expression("log"[2] * "(fold change) RNA-seq")
  ) +
  theme_bw()
